      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00286"/>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur
                  Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb168940" type="place">Spöttelgasse 7</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00287"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb304404" type="place">Königsberg</rs></hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print">Partie am <rs type="place" ref="#pmb169721">Pregel</rs> und Blick
                  auf den <rs type="place" ref="#pmb136">Dom</rs></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00286"/><date>2. Dez. 09</date></seg><salute>Lieber Arthur!</salute></opener><p>Heute hier im <rs ref="#pmb29667" type="org">Goethebund</rs>:<lb/>Schnitzlerabend von
               HermannBahr.</p><p><anchor type="label" xml:id="LL323-1">So bin ich unermüdlich um Deinen Ruhm in Nord
                  u. Süd be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>orgt.</anchor></p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t, mit<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chönen Grüßen an <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173" subtype="implied">Frau</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12692" subtype="implied">Sohn</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2238" subtype="implied">Tochter</rs>,<lb/>Dein<lb/><signed>H<unclear>m</unclear>B.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
